[
  {
    "startTime": 0.33,
    "endTime": 3.306,
    "text": "- Oh no, oh no, there's too many."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.306,
    "endTime": 5.806,
    "text": "(light music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.37,
    "endTime": 10.1,
    "text": "OK, so today we are gonna melt all 100 chocolate bars"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.1,
    "endTime": 13.363,
    "text": "into the one epic chocolate bar, hopefully."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.37,
    "endTime": 14.363999999999999,
    "text": "Let's get started."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.365,
    "endTime": 15.765,
    "text": "I'll move these to the side."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.329,
    "endTime": 17.162,
    "text": "Oh no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.172,
    "endTime": 19.42,
    "text": "(pots clanking)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.42,
    "endTime": 21.393,
    "text": "I've got a little bit of water."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.56,
    "endTime": 23.25,
    "text": "Which I'm gonna start boiling."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.25,
    "endTime": 25.323,
    "text": "Um, how do I start this thing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.77,
    "endTime": 28.23,
    "text": "Wow, cool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.9,
    "endTime": 32.65,
    "text": "So I guess I'll just start unwrapping the chocolates."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.65,
    "endTime": 34.309,
    "text": "I'm just gonna chat with Tasty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.31,
    "endTime": 36.97,
    "text": "You think, Matt, a Tasty producer, should just pop in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.97,
    "endTime": 38.943,
    "text": "to make sure I'm doing this right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.95,
    "endTime": 41.35,
    "text": "- Wow, this is a lot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.35,
    "endTime": 43.870000000000005,
    "text": "I didn't know there was this many candy bars in the world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.87,
    "endTime": 44.769,
    "text": "- I don't want to mess it up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.77,
    "endTime": 45.690000000000005,
    "text": "You don't mind helping?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.69,
    "endTime": 46.522,
    "text": "- No, I'd love to."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.523,
    "endTime": 48.190000000000005,
    "text": "- I'm gonna start throwing wrappers on the ground."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.19,
    "endTime": 49.22,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.26,
    "endTime": 51.973,
    "text": "- Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.26,
    "endTime": 53.93,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.476,
    "endTime": 54.309,
    "text": "You know, what a lie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.309,
    "endTime": 55.379,
    "text": "They're supposed to be candy bars."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.38,
    "endTime": 58.379000000000005,
    "text": "York, that's kind of a weird flavor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.379,
    "endTime": 59.211,
    "text": "- Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.212,
    "endTime": 60.790000000000006,
    "text": "It's not gonna taste good, I don't think."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.79,
    "endTime": 62.952,
    "text": "- Oh, I've been very excited about this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.574,
    "endTime": 67.649,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.65,
    "endTime": 68.483,
    "text": "I'm into it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.483,
    "endTime": 69.316,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.316,
    "endTime": 70.973,
    "text": "Are we being exciting and fun?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.8,
    "endTime": 73.676,
    "text": "- It's time to start giving it a little bit of a mix."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.677,
    "endTime": 76.28,
    "text": "- OK, it does look like (car honking) literally."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.28,
    "endTime": 77.52,
    "text": "- Yeah. (laughing)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.52,
    "endTime": 78.39,
    "text": "But it'll taste good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.39,
    "endTime": 80.578,
    "text": "This one is chili so it's gonna be a little bit spicy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.578,
    "endTime": 81.411,
    "text": "- Mm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.16,
    "endTime": 83.429,
    "text": "This one has cornflakes in it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.43,
    "endTime": 85.49000000000001,
    "text": "- Opening some of these is bringing back my childhood"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.49,
    "endTime": 87.399,
    "text": "insecurities of not being able to open up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.4,
    "endTime": 89.46300000000001,
    "text": "Watch you do it in one second, one try."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.385,
    "endTime": 93.635,
    "text": "(laughing)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.6,
    "endTime": 97.5,
    "text": "We're on the home stretch. - We are."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.5,
    "endTime": 99.673,
    "text": "- And I'm ending with good 'ol Three Musketeers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.12,
    "endTime": 101.183,
    "text": "- All right, classic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.69,
    "endTime": 102.83,
    "text": "- I think that should be stirred."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.83,
    "endTime": 103.899,
    "text": "But I don't think it will all fit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.9,
    "endTime": 104.87,
    "text": "So why don't I get another bowl."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.87,
    "endTime": 106.56,
    "text": "Wow, sensual."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.56,
    "endTime": 107.53,
    "text": "So I'm gonna go back up and shoot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.53,
    "endTime": 110.48,
    "text": "But once this is fully melted pour that one"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.48,
    "endTime": 112.94,
    "text": "into one of those and then let them chill"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.0,
    "endTime": 114.25,
    "text": "in the fridge or freezer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.94,
    "endTime": 115.773,
    "text": "- Not this one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.773,
    "endTime": 116.606,
    "text": "- OK, got it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.606,
    "endTime": 118.199,
    "text": "So I'll check back on you later, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.2,
    "endTime": 119.193,
    "text": "- Yes, please do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.74,
    "endTime": 120.93299999999999,
    "text": "Chocolate soup."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.19,
    "endTime": 122.583,
    "text": "Chocolate soup."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.83,
    "endTime": 126.3,
    "text": "You guys want to try it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.63,
    "endTime": 127.603,
    "text": "So delicious."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.66,
    "endTime": 128.883,
    "text": "It tastes like frosting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.82,
    "endTime": 131.653,
    "text": "- It's very minty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.653,
    "endTime": 133.23,
    "text": "- Think it would fit in this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.1,
    "endTime": 134.25,
    "text": "We're just gonna do it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.6,
    "endTime": 137.34,
    "text": "There's some interesting chunks at the bottom of this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.34,
    "endTime": 139.473,
    "text": "Some wafer, peanuts."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.0,
    "endTime": 141.72,
    "text": "You're right, this is a good size."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.72,
    "endTime": 142.972,
    "text": "I'll get this one going."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.2,
    "endTime": 146.76,
    "text": "This one does have different bars."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.76,
    "endTime": 147.593,
    "text": "You can tell."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.593,
    "endTime": 148.426,
    "text": "Alright."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.426,
    "endTime": 149.57,
    "text": "Put it in the refrige."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.733,
    "endTime": 151.293,
    "text": "Oh if I make it safely."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.4,
    "endTime": 155.57,
    "text": "So while the other chocolate is getting cold,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.57,
    "endTime": 157.778,
    "text": "I'm gonna melt this chocolate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.778,
    "endTime": 160.343,
    "text": "I don't have anything to say while it's melting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.389,
    "endTime": 163.389,
    "text": "(crickets chirping)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.469,
    "endTime": 166.719,
    "text": "Oh, it's solid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.51,
    "endTime": 170.343,
    "text": "- Yeah"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.85,
    "endTime": 172.653,
    "text": "I'll just rest it on my bump."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.72,
    "endTime": 174.373,
    "text": "And then head off."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.485,
    "endTime": 178.97000000000003,
    "text": "I don't feel super good about this next step."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.97,
    "endTime": 181.53,
    "text": "Let's go, upstairs, maybe Matt will be there"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.53,
    "endTime": 182.543,
    "text": "and he'll help us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.67,
    "endTime": 185.232,
    "text": "We found him, he's up here, he's making sushi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.246,
    "endTime": 188.0,
    "text": "I think I need a big sheet pan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.0,
    "endTime": 188.88,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.88,
    "endTime": 189.713,
    "text": "- Well wait."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.96,
    "endTime": 193.113,
    "text": "So you're taking the one from the freezer on to here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.1,
    "endTime": 196.843,
    "text": "- OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.7,
    "endTime": 200.57,
    "text": "- Oh yeah, look at that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.84,
    "endTime": 203.803,
    "text": "Let's put a little pool of it in the center."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.36,
    "endTime": 205.24,
    "text": "I'm feeling good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.24,
    "endTime": 206.19500000000002,
    "text": "I think we're good to go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.195,
    "endTime": 207.528,
    "text": "Three, two, one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 532.2,
    "endTime": 534.589,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 534.589,
    "endTime": 535.7600000000001,
    "text": "- It's pretty on this side."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 535.76,
    "endTime": 544.17,
    "text": "- Yeah, now I think you should do the honors."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 544.17,
    "endTime": 554.03,
    "text": "- OK, oh, wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 554.03,
    "endTime": 560.769,
    "text": "It worked out like the right amount."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 560.769,
    "endTime": 569.03,
    "text": "How did that happen?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 569.03,
    "endTime": 571.579,
    "text": "- So now I say that we put it into the fridge."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 571.579,
    "endTime": 579.1999999999999,
    "text": "- So are you gonna come back and eat it in an hour?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 579.2,
    "endTime": 582.2900000000001,
    "text": "- I will try part of it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 582.29,
    "endTime": 587.05,
    "text": "- Ta-da!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 587.05,
    "endTime": 591.12,
    "text": "Matt come look at this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 591.12,
    "endTime": 599.839,
    "text": "It did crack a little."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 599.839,
    "endTime": 606.36,
    "text": "But you know, I still feel like it's beautiful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 606.36,
    "endTime": 609.86,
    "text": "Alright, going for it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 609.86,
    "endTime": 618.8100000000001,
    "text": "Mm, taste great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 618.81,
    "endTime": 624.27,
    "text": "- Oh do I have to do it too?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 624.27,
    "endTime": 630.18,
    "text": "It's like chewy on the inside."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 630.18,
    "endTime": 634.9899999999999,
    "text": "- This is delicious."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 634.99,
    "endTime": 647.1,
    "text": "Oh it's kind of peanut buttery."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 647.1,
    "endTime": 646.1800000000001,
    "text": "- I'm getting coconut too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 646.18,
    "endTime": 652.3389999999999,
    "text": "And a little bit of everything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 652.339,
    "endTime": 660.149,
    "text": "- Alright guys!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 660.149,
    "endTime": 664.589,
    "text": "- Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 664.589,
    "endTime": 673.11,
    "text": "- [Everyone] Wow!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 673.11,
    "endTime": 675.0600000000001,
    "text": "(laughing)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 675.06,
    "endTime": 680.6999999999999,
    "text": "- Well, see ya."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 675.06,
    "endTime": 680.6999999999999,
    "text": "- This is good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 680.7,
    "endTime": 685.73,
    "text": "- It's great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 685.73,
    "endTime": 693.72,
    "text": "- Legit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 693.72,
    "endTime": 696.4200000000001,
    "text": "It's happy hour."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 696.42,
    "endTime": 703.2099999999999,
    "text": "- Today when the day started, I did not expect to be here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 703.21,
    "endTime": 707.48,
    "text": "- Yep."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 707.48,
    "endTime": 712.64,
    "text": "- But we did it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 712.64,
    "endTime": 717.6999999999999,
    "text": "And it's actually pretty impressive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 717.7,
    "endTime": 724.4200000000001,
    "text": "- I'm kind of over chocolate right now though."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 724.42,
    "endTime": 730.389,
    "text": "- Yeah, I don't think I'd ever want to see it again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 730.389,
    "endTime": 734.1800000000001,
    "text": "(laughing)"
  }
]